        "timestamp": "2017-07-18 12:13:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nI don't see an installation mechanism provided -- in order to test this, I manually created 'features', 'features/healthcheck' and 'features/eelf', and did the unzips. Perhaps there should be a 'features install <file>' option to the 'features' script. Also, the script should print out usage information, even if the 'features' directory does not exist (rather than just 'no features').",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
